dc_title_s: Offshore Wind Energy Planning - Marine Jurisdictions: Maryland
dc_description_s: This is a MD iMAP hosted service layer. Find more information at http://imap.maryland.gov. The NOAA Coastal Services Center's Marine Jurisdiction dataset was created to assist in marine spatial planning and offshore alternative energy sitting. This is a composite dataset derived from a collection of authoritative marine boundary data provided by the DIO Minerals Management Service and the NOAA Office of Coast Survey. NOT LEGALLY BINDING. This dataset is not an authoritative data source for marine boundaries, please see the Minerals Management Service and NOAA Office of Coast Survey for authoritative data and more comprehensive use constraints. Last Updated: Unknown
